                <a href="map-of-sicily-original.jpg" title="Click to see the enlarged map of Sicily">
                    <img class="odd" src="map-of-sicily.jpg" alt="Map of Sicily" />
                </a>
                <p>I lived in Sicily for only about 6 months. I've been to a few places in Italy -
                   like Rome, Naples, Sorrento. But I happened to actually live in a small coastal town in Sicily -
                   Oliveri. It's located on the North shore near Messina. Me and my husband got married there
                   and started our life together. My father-in-law was born and spent his young years in Sicily.
                   For this reason my husband was visiting Sicily a lot.
                   Italy is such a famous travel destination these days that I can hardly be original here.
                </p>
            </article>
            <article>
                <p>Sicily is paradise on Earth. In my opinion this is the place where you have to rent a
                   car and just drive, drive, drive. Here are some photos I took around Oliveri when I lived there.
                </p>
            </article>
